        "section_sub": "",
        "description": "<p>Here at Paez, we love the fresh start that a spring/summer season provides because we're all about new beginnings. This year, we Blossom towards becoming our best and most inspiring versions. We challenged portuguese stylist, Carolina Canas, to create looks inspired by our shoes, that could be a perfect match to our espadrilles, or our Mary Janes, Sandals, Mocs and Mules!</p>",
